<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Anmelden · Votepit</title>
    <style>
        :root { --accent: #3b82f6; }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, system-ui, sans-serif;
            color: #0f172a;
            background: #f8fafc;
            line-height: 1.5;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }
        .wrap { max-width: 420px; margin: 12vh auto; padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem; }
        .card {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 2rem 2.25rem;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(15, 23, 42, .04);
        }
        h1 { margin: 0 0 .25rem; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -.01em; }
        p.lead { color: #475569; margin: .5rem 0 1.5rem; font-size: .95rem; }
        label { display: block; font-size: .875rem; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: .4rem; }
        input[type="email"] {
            width: 100%; padding: .6rem .8rem; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; outline: none;
            transition: border-color .15s;
        }
        input[type="email"]:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
        button {
            margin-top: 1rem; width: 100%; padding: .65rem 1rem;
            background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border: none;
            border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer; transition: background .15s;
        }
        button:hover { background: #2563eb; }
        footer { margin-top: 1.5rem; color: #94a3b8; font-size: .8rem; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main class="wrap">
        <section class="card">
            <h1>Anmelden</h1>
            <p class="lead">Gib deine E-Mail-Adresse ein. Wir schicken dir einen Magic-Link.</p>
            <form method="POST" action="/login">
                <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{ csrf_token }}">
                <label for="email">E-Mail-Adresse</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required autocomplete="email" autofocus placeholder="du@example.com">
                <button type="submit">Magic-Link senden</button>
            </form>
        </section>
        <footer>Votepit · Passwortlos anmelden</footer>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
